  "detailed_description": "<h1>DLC for Fernbus Sim + Tourist Bus Sim</h1><p>By purchasing this DLC you will also receive <a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/724440/Fernbus_Simulator__VDL_Futura_FHD2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Touris Bus Simulator - VDL Futura FHD2</a>:<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/953681/extras/capsule_sm_FBS.jpg?t=1554806205\" > <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/953681/extras/capsule_sm_TBS.jpg?t=1554806205\" ></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>This DLC brings the whole range of the VDL Futura FHD2 - six variations from the most compact to the largest, two axles or three axles - to your fleet. With the official license from VDL, we were able to develop this digital version of the Futura FHD2 in authentic detail, and not just visually but also acoustic and technically functional to the original real-world vehicle.<br><br>The manufacturer from Eindhoven, Netherlands, has focused on comfort, safety and efficiency. The FHD2 range is the company's specialist for luxury journeys. From day trips to multi-day trips abroad. The modular and lightweight designs allow for a wide variety of constructions which excels in economic profitability.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">All 6 variants included:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Futura FHD2-106<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-122<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-129<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-135<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-139<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-148</li></ul><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/953681/extras/Features.jpg?t=1554806205\" ><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Official license of VDL<br></li><li>Detailed exterior and walk-in interior<br></li><li>12-gear automatic transmission<br></li><li>Cruise control and retarder<br></li><li>Reactive displays, e.g. with information about speed and readiness for departure<br></li><li>Detailed, interactive cockpit with extensive functionality and various camera perspectives.<br></li><li>Functional online radio, air conditioning and other service features<br></li><li>Driver monitor with navigation and rear view camera<br></li><li>Kneeling system<br></li><li>A complete lighting system of interior and exterior<br></li><li>Usable driver windows and sun shield<br></li><li>Interactive controls for the doors and luggage compartment hatches<br></li><li>Download or upload custom community paint jobs via Steam Workshop</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "This DLC brings the whole range of the VDL Futura FHD2 - six variations from the most compact to the largest, two axles or three axles - to your fleet. With the official license from VDL, we were able to develop this digital version of the Futura FHD2 in authentic detail, and not just visually but also acoustic and technically functional to the original real-world vehicle.<br><br>The manufacturer from Eindhoven, Netherlands, has focused on comfort, safety and efficiency. The FHD2 range is the company's specialist for luxury journeys. From day trips to multi-day trips abroad. The modular and lightweight designs allow for a wide variety of constructions which excels in economic profitability.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">All 6 variants included:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Futura FHD2-106<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-122<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-129<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-135<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-139<br></li><li>Futura FHD2-148</li></ul><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/953681/extras/Features.jpg?t=1554806205\" ><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Official license of VDL<br></li><li>Detailed exterior and walk-in interior<br></li><li>12-gear automatic transmission<br></li><li>Cruise control and retarder<br></li><li>Reactive displays, e.g. with information about speed and readiness for departure<br></li><li>Detailed, interactive cockpit with extensive functionality and various camera perspectives.<br></li><li>Functional online radio, air conditioning and other service features<br></li><li>Driver monitor with navigation and rear view camera<br></li><li>Kneeling system<br></li><li>A complete lighting system of interior and exterior<br></li><li>Usable driver windows and sun shield<br></li><li>Interactive controls for the doors and luggage compartment hatches<br></li><li>Download or upload custom community paint jobs via Steam Workshop</li></ul>",
